lled%20%26quot%3BEyeConnect%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20lets%20two%20wearers%20launch%20shared%20experiences%20simply%20by%20making%20eye%20contact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%C2%A0that%20might%20not%20be%20enough%20of%20a%20differentiator%20given%20the%20massive%20price%20tag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSnap%20Specs%20for%20%242%2C195%20is%20an%20instant%20nope%20for%2099%25%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ray%20Wong%2C%20senior%20editor%20of%20Gizmodo%2C%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaj%20Nijjer%2C%20the%20CMO%20of%20Symmetry%20Software%2C%20called%20the%20Specs%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20touch%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20Riley%20Brown%2C%20a%20tech%20educator%20and%20startup%20founder%2C%20posted%20on%20X%20that%20the%20Specs%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bdead%20on%20arrival.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20pair%20of%20Specs%20also%20weighs%20around%20132%20grams%2C%20nearly%20twice%20that%20of%20Meta's%20Ray-Bans%2C%20which%20weigh%20around%2070%20grams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Specs%20on%20display%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a31ac8c2bbd1d834ef244c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222194%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESnap's%20Specs%20cost%20%242%2C195%20and%20will%20ship%20by%20fall%202026.%3Cp%3EPhillip%20Faraone%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Snap%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESpecs%20arrive%20as%20Meta%20has%20established%20an%20early%20lead%20with%20its%20Ray-Ban%20partnership%2C%20while%20Google%20recently%20unveiled%20its%20own%20AI-powered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-competing-with-meta-ray-bans-new-warby-parker-partnership-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeyewear%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20problem%20dogging%20the%20tech%20is%20that%20no%20one%20has%20cracked%20the%20economics.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-apple-mark-zuckerberg-vr-ar-market-idc-matthew-ball-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta's%20