0ZDF%20tied%20Elon%20Musk%20to%20unrest%20in%20Northern%20Ireland.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20said%20he%20planned%20to%20take%20legal%20action%20over%20%26quot%3Boutrageous%20lies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EZDF%20has%20now%20removed%20the%20language%20that%20angered%20Musk.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20achieved%20an%20initial%20win%20in%20his%20dispute%20with%20Germany's%20public%20broadcaster%20ZDF%3A%20The%20network%20said%20it%20would%20remove%20language%20about%20Musk's%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fnorthern-ireland-belfast-stabbing-violence-1d8b2331cfa33a0b39492ca9098c206f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunrest%20in%20Northern%20Ireland%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20program%20that%20aired%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20Musk%20is%20a%20controversial%20figure%20for%20German%20media%20is%20probably%20nothing%20new%20to%20the%20tech%20entrepreneur.%20But%20now%20he%20appears%20to%20have%20had%20enough%20of%20ZDF.%20On%20Monday%20evening%2C%20he%20announced%20on%20X%20that%20he%20would%20take%20%26quot%3Blegal%20action%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20public%20broadcaster%20over%20what%20he%20called%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F2066565993040593115%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Boutrageous%20lies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trigger%20was%20the%20introduction%20to%20the%20June%2012%20edition%20of%20the%20program%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zdfheute.de%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZDFheute%20Live%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20presenter%20Christina%20von%20Ungern-Sternberg%20stated%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20brutal%20attempted%20murder%20in%20broad%20daylight%20in%20Belfast.%20Someone%20records%20it%2C%20the%20video%20goes%20viral.%20A%20racist%20mob%20then%20hunts%20migrants.%20The%20call%20to%20action%20came%20from%20a%20British%20far-right%20extremist%20and%20tech%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20had%20not%20called%20for%20a%20hunt%20against%20migrants%3B%20he%20had%20shared%20a%20call%20for%20a%20demonstration%20posted%20by%20a%20far-right%20extremist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emergency%20vehicles%20converge%20on%20fires%20in%20Belfast%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a31b2d24074dae0e2044604%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFires%20burn%20in%20Glengormley%2C%20north%20of%20Belfast%2C%20after%20unrest%20that%20authorities%20blamed%20on%20far-right%20activists.%3Cp%3EPaul%20Faith%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20WELT%20reported%20that%20Hamburg-based%20attorney%20Joachim%20Steinh%C3%B6fel%20had%20sent%20a%20legal%20warning%20letter%20to%20the%20broadcaster%20on%20Musk's%20behalf.%20Around%202%20p.m.%2C%20ZDF%20confirmed%20that%20it%20had%20complied%20with%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20cease-and-desist%20declaration%20and%20told%20WELT%3A%20%26quot%3BZDF%20has%20submitted%20the%20declaration%20and%20removed%20the%20passage%20in%20question%20from%20the%20introduction.%20As%20early%20as%20Saturday%2C%20ZDF%20had%20already%20added%20a%20transparency%20notice%20correcting%20the%20broadcast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20cease-and-desist%20declaration%2C%20the%20broadcaster%20avoided%20a%20formal%20injunction%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20be%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20longer%20dispute%20between%20Musk%20and%20ZDF.%20Earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Steinh%C3%B6fel%20told%20%3Cem%3EWELT%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20phone%20that%20he%20intended%20to%20propose%20that%20Musk%20review%20all%20ZDF%20reports%20about%20him%20from%20recent%20years%E2%80%94%26quot%3Bat%20least%20those%20that%20are%20not%20yet%20time-barred%26quot%3B%E2%80%94for%20potential%20legal%20violations%20and%20pursue%20claims%20where%20appropriate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20case%20in%20which%20ZDF%20has%20commented%20on%20my%20client%20in%20a%20questionable%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20Steinh%C3%B6fel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225568%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Demonstrators%20fill%20a%20Belfast%20street%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a31b3942bbd1d834ef2452f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDemonstrators%20attend%20a%20United%20Against%20Racism%20rally%20on%20June%2013%2C%202026%20in%20Belfast%2C%20after%20recent%20unrest.%3Cp%3ECharles%20McQuillan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20could%20also%20demand%20a%20correction%20or%20seek%20damages%20from%20ZDF.%20Tobias%20Gostomzyk%2C%20professor%20of%20Media%20Law%20at%20TU%20Dortmund%2C%20said%20he%20should%20not%20expect%20major%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMusk%20would%20have%20to%20specifically%20demonstrate%20and%20prove%20that%20the%20reporting%20caused%20him%20a%20measurable%20economic%20loss%20and%20that%20this%20loss%20was%20causally%20linked%20to%20the%20contested%20statement.%20In%20practice%2C%20such%20proof%20would%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20provide%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20professor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20could%20make%20a%20claim%20for%20monetary%20compensation%20based%20on%20a%20violation%20of%20his%20general%20personality%20rights.%20According%20to%20established%20case%20law%2C%20such%20compensation%20is%20granted%20only%20in%20cases%20of%20serious%20violations%20that%20cannot%20be%20adequately%20remedied%20by%20other%20means%2C%20such%20as%20a%20correction%2C%20a%20right%20of%20reply%2C%20or%20an%20injunction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20the%20requirements%20were%20considered%20fulfilled%20in%20this%20case%2C%20any%20monetary%20compensation%20would%20likely%20be%20relatively%20modest%2C%26quot%3B%20Gostomzyk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20could%20also%20file%20suit%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLegal%20action%20against%20ZDF%20in%20the%20United%20States%20would%20be%20conceivable%20if%20the%20report%20was%20received%20there.%20Given%20Elon%20Musk's%20prominence%2C%20that%20seems%20likely.%20Many%20Germans%2C%20including%20significant%20investors%2C%20live%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20Steinh%C3%B6fel%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20not%20personally%20handling%20that%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHans-J%C3%BCrgen%20Homann%2C%20who%20is%20licensed%20to%20practice%20law%20in%20both%20Germany%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20said%20Musk's%20legal%20position%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20figure%26quot%3B%20would%20likely%20be%20weaker%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%20enjoys%20broader%20protection%20than%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20originally%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.welt.de%2Fpolitik%2Fdeutschland%2Fplus6a3166c57e682fc37fbfcab8%2Ffalschbehauptung-in-diesem-punkt-duerfte-elon-musks-vorgehen-gegen-das-zdf-keinen-erfolg-haben.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eappeared%20on%20WELT%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Eand%20is%20courtesy%20of%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20Global%20Reporters%20Network%2C%20which%20harnesses%20the%20resources%20of%20the%20company's%20newsrooms%20to%20publish%20ambitious%20scoops%2C%20investigations%2C%20interviews%2C%20opinion%20pieces%2C%20and%20analysis.%20It%20allows%20journalists%20%E2%80%94%20including%20those%20from%20POLITICO%2C%20Business%20Insider%2C%20WELT%2C%20BILD%2C%20Onet%2C%20and%20Fakt%20%E2%80%94%20to%20collaborate%20on%20major%20stories%20for%20an%20international%20audience%20of%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20across%20platforms.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgermanys-zdf-removes-language-tying-elon-musk-to-belfast-unrest-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781642697000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a31afc32bbd1d834ef244fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgermanys-zdf-removes-language-tying-elon-musk-to-belfast-unrest-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Musk%20threatened%20legal%20action%20against%20ZDF%20for%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Boutrageous%20lies.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Insider%20Inc.)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Government%3A%20No%20cough%20syrup%20sale%20without%20prescription%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781642421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131781395%2Cimgsize-832591.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fgovernment-no-cough-syrup-sale-sans-prescription%2Farticleshow%2F131781393.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cough%20syrups%20will%20now%20require%20a%20doctor's%20prescription%20as%20the%20Centre%20has%20removed%20them%20from%20a%20decades-old%20exemption.%20This%20move%2C%20following%20concerns%20over%20contaminated%20syrups%2C%20brings%20all%20formulations%20under%20regular%20regulatory%20oversight.%20The%20change%20aims%20to%20enhance%20accountability%20and%20public%20health%20safety%20in%20the%20distribution%20of%20these%20commonly%20used%20medicines.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ANUJA%20JAISWAL%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20techie%20Sai%20Karthik%20Varma%20Datla%20among%2012%20people%20killed%20in%20Missouri%20plane%20crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781642115000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131781385%2Cimgsize-84072.cms%22%2C%