%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meta's%20CTO%20says%20morale%20is%20almost%20'the%20worst%20it's%20ever%20been'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meta%20CTO%20Andrew%20Bosworth.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a319a684074dae0e204446a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222662%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeta%20CTO%20Andrew%20Bosworth.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMorale%20at%20Meta%20is%20near%20an%20all-time%20low%2C%20chief%20technical%20officer%20Andrew%20%26quot%3BBoz%26quot%3B%20Bosworth%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Cambridge%20Analytica%20scandal%20was%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20the%20worst%26quot%3B%20time%20in%20terms%20of%20morale%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20aims%20to%20boost%20morale%20with%20career%20development%20and%20other%20initiatives%20post-layoffs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vibes%20are%20off%20at%20Meta%2C%20its%20top%20leadership%20said%20internally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20chief%20technology%20officer%20Andrew%20%26quot%3BBoz%26quot%3B%20Bosworth%20said%20morale%20at%20the%20tech%20giant%20is%20near%20an%20all-time%20low%20as%20recent%20mass%20layoffs%20and%20internal%20AI%20initiatives%20roil%20many%20longtime%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorale%20is%20%26quot%3Bmaybe%20not%20the%20worst%20it's%20ever%20been%20in%2020%20years%20here%2C%20but%20it's%20probably%20up%20there.%20It's%20definitely%20up%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Bosworth%20said%20during%20an%20internal%20%26quot%3BTuesdays%20with%20Boz%26quot%3B%20chat%20on%20June%202%2C%20four%20people%20who%20were%20on%20the%20call%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20think%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcambridge-analytica-a-guide-to-the-trump-linked-data-firm-that-harvested-50-million-facebook-profiles-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECambridge%20Analytica%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20probably%20the%20worst%2C%26quot%3B%20Bosworth%20added%20in%20reference%20to%20the%20scandal%20about%20millions%20of%20Facebook%20users'%20data%20being%20used%20to%20target%20voters%20during%20the%202016%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20added%20that%20morale%20is%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20it's%20ever%20been.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20difficult%20year%20for%20many%20Meta%20employees.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-meta-layoff-email-employees-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20laid%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%2010%25%20of%20staff%20in%20May%2C%20citing%20the%20need%20to%20offset%20its%20huge%20AI%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-task-force-workers-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20reassigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20roughly%20another%2010%25%20of%20its%20workforce%20to%20train%20its%20AI%20models.%20Some%20staff%20referred%20to%20joining%20the%20mandatory%20task%20force%20as%20being%20%26quot%3Bdrafted%26quot%3B%20and%20viewed%20the%20work%20largely%20as%20data-labeling%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20Meta%20also%20faced%20employee%20backlash%20over%20an%20initiative%20to%20track%20their%20mouse%20movements%20and%20keystrokes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-new-ai-tool-tracks-staff-activity-sparks-concern-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimprove%20Meta's%20AI%20models%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20leadership%20said%20it%20has%20begun%20taking%20steps%20to%20improve%20morale.%20On%20Monday%2C%20Bosworth%20sent%20a%20memo%20to%20staff%20about%20how%20Meta%20needs%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20the%20best%20place%20for%20the%20best%20people%20to%20do%20their%20best%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20hoped%20to%20%26quot%3Brekindle%20the%20best%20of%20the%20culture%26quot%3B%20that%20people%20joined%2C%20according%20to%20a%20copy%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20which%20was%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fandrew-bosworth-meta-employees-unrest%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20by%20Wired%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20provide%20our%20people%20the%20support%20to%20do%20things%20the%20right%20way%20for%20the%20long%20term%2C%20including%20taking%20smart%20risks%20when%20the%20situation%20calls%20for%20it%20and%20to%20be%20recognized%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20will%20commit%20to%20transparency%20from%20its%20leadership%20and%20its%20employees'%20personal%20and%20career%20development%2C%20Bosworth's%20post%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20will%20allow%20people%20reassigned%20to%20the%20AI%20task%20force%20to%20reapply%20for%20other%20jobs%20within%20Meta%20if%20they%20want%20to%2C%20and%20it%20is%20increasing%20budgets%20for%20travel%2C%20events%2C%20and%20snacks%2C%20Wired%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acrollet%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ecrollet%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20on%20Signal%20and%20WhatsApp%20at%20%3Cu%3E628-282-2811%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3Cem%3E%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecure-news-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-cto-andrew-bosworth-addresses-morale-aft