carriers%20are%20seeing%20favorable%20supply-and-demand%20dynamics%2C%20partly%20driven%20by%20the%20war.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAirline%20CEOs%20aren't%20dismissing%20that%20lower%20oil%20prices%20may%20not%20lower%20fares.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFlyers%20hoping%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwizz-air-iran-war-making-people-book-their-vacations-later-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeaper%20flights%20this%20summer%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20be%20disappointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOil%20prices%20%E2%80%94%20airlines'%20second-largest%20expense%20after%20labor%20%E2%80%94%20have%20tumbled%20below%20%2480%20a%20barrel%20from%20highs%20above%20%24100%20after%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20announced%20a%20preliminary%20agreement%20to%20end%20the%20nearly%20four-month%20war%20that%20closed%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20a%20vital%20artery%20for%20global%20oil%20shipments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAviation%20analysts%20say%20airlines%20won't%20rush%20to%20cut%20ticket%20prices%20or%20their%20lucrative%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funited-airlines-checked-baggage-fees-jetblue-fuel-price-rise-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echecked-bag%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20if%20the%20war%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20ends%3B%20another%20wrinkle%20is%20that%20Israel%20is%20not%20a%20direct%20party%20to%20the%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20US%20and%20Israel%20launched%20the%20conflict%20in%20late%20February%2C%20carriers%20have%20cut%20unprofitable%20routes%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-airlines-pay-fuel-planes-fares-impact-oil-iran-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20fares%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ancillary%20fees%20to%20offset%20higher%20fuel%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Aboulafia%2C%20aviation%20analyst%20and%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20AeroDynamic%20Advisory%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20tight%20seat%20supply%2C%20combined%20with%20resilient%20demand%2C%20has%20given%20airlines%20little%20incentive%20to%20reverse%20course%20on%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThings%20are%20pretty%20good%2C%20maybe%20traffic%20is%20down%20a%20little%2C%20but%20profits%20aren't%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20why%20would%20you%3F%20Inflation%20is%20a%20great%20excuse%20to%20get%20more%20pricing%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20KAYAK%20flight%20search%20shows%20that%20average%20domestic%20airfares%20are%20up%20about%208%25%20since%20the%20war%20started%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchart-rising-fuel-costs-make-plane-ticket-more-expensive-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaverage%20international%20airfares%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20up%20about%2018%25.%20Fares%20from%20the%20US%20to%20Amsterdam%20and%20London%2C%20for%20example%2C%20have%20increased%20by%20more%20than%20%24200%20roundtrip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20airlines%20have%20also%20raised%20checked%20bag%20fees%20by%20as%20much%20as%20%2450%20one-way%20to%20offset%20soaring%20oil%20prices%2C%20with%20most%20major%20carriers%20now%20charging%20between%20%2440%20and%20%2450%20per%20bag%20each%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-airline-ceos-are-saying-iran-war-impact-flights-prices-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirline%20CEOs%20at%20Delta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20United%2C%20and%20Southwest%20aren't%20disputing%20analysts'%20warnings%2C%20saying%20resilient%20demand%2C%20tight%20capacity%2C%20and%20durable%20pricing%20power%20are%20reasons%20fares%20are%20likely%20to%20remain%20elevated%20even%20if%20oil%20prices%20ease%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20and%20our%20competitors%20are%20all%20focused%20on%20ratable%20production%20of%20results%2C%20steady%20production%20of%20results%2C%20sustainable%20margins%2C%20and%20so%20I%20do%20think%20that%20produces%20a%20backdrop%20where%20we'll%20certainly%20not%20attempt%20to%20give%20some%20of%20these%20fare%20increases%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Southwest%20CEO%20Bob%20Jordan%20said%20at%20the%20Bernstein%20Strategic%20Decisions%20Conference%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226faaaa87-f847-4adc-969a-1a787ffecee6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20expect%20flight%20prices%20to%20drop%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERaymond%20James%20analyst%20Savanthi%20Sath%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairline-points-miles-book-flights-vacation-travel-gurus-prices-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eairline%20ticket%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fall%2C%20supply%20needs%20to%20increase%20or%20demand%20needs%20to%20soften%20%E2%80%94%20but%20she%20said%20that's%20unlikely%2C%20especially%20since%20oil%20is%20still%20up%2050%25%20year-over-year%20and%20oil%20shocks%20may%20continue%20even%20with%20a%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCapacity%20through%20August%20is%20likely%20mostly%20finalized%20by%20now%2C%20so%20the%20opportunity%20to%20gain%20confidence%20to%20add%20back%20more%20capacity%20(or%20get%20back%20to%20the%20prior%20plan)%20would%20be%20in%204Q%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20that%20begins%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20has%20repeatedly%20announced%20possible%20deals%20to%20end%20the%20war%2C%20but%20many%20ultimately%20fell%20through.%20The%20latest%20agreement%20is%20moving%20to%20a%20Friday%20signing%2C%20but%20may%20leave%20key%20issues%20unresolved%2C%20like%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20Iran's%20highly%20enriched%20uranium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224134%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Donald%20Trump%20speaks%20as%20U.S.%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20(L)%20listens%20during%20a%20Cabinet%20meeting%20in%20the%20Cabinet%20Room%20of%20the%20White%20House.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a319558564c774507cd3130%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222756%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Trump%20Administration%20is%20expected%20to%20sign%20an%20agreement%20with%20Iran%20at%20a%20Friday%20ceremony%20in%20Switzerland.%3Cp%3EWin%20McNamee%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20have%20spoken%20about%20the%20deal%20in%20broad%20statements%2C%20but%20its%20specific%20terms%20remain%20secret.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fbulletin%2Fnews%2Ftrump-iran-nuclear-weapons-peace-deal-b2996570.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarned%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20if%20Iran%20were%20to%20acquire%20a%20nuclear%20weapon%2C%20%26quot%3Ball%20hell%20will%20rain%20down%20on%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETime%20will%20tell%20how%20durable%20the%20US-Iran%20agreement%20proves%20to%20be%2C%20and%20some%20airlines%20may%20be%20hedging%20their%20bets.%20United%20CEO%20Scott%20Kirby%20told%20Bloomberg%20at%20an%20industry%20conference%20in%20early%20June%20that%20he%20is%20not%20confident%20any%20deal%20to%20reopen%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20would%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESath%20added%20that%20airlines%20in%20general%20may%20also%20be%20hesitant%20to%20add%20capacity%20after%20a%20series%20of%20shocks%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20including%20persistent%20inflation%20that%20has%20driven%20up%20operating%20costs%20and%20two%20government%20shutdowns%20that%20caused%20mass%20flight%20delays%20and%20cancellations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENerdWallet%20travel%20analyst%20Sally%20French%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20pricing%20picture%20also%20has%20to%20factor%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspirit-airlines-collapses-shuts-down-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpirit%20Airlines'%20collapse%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20its%20cheaper%20tickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20fewer%20seats%20and%20one%20fewer%20ultra-low-cost%20carrier%2C%20we're%20generally%20not%20seeing%20the%20kind%20of%20downward%20pressure%20on%20fares%20that%20budget-conscious%20travelers%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20checked%20bag%20fees%2C%20all%20three%20analysts%20say%20they%20are%20unlikely%20to%20drop.%20Data%20from%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Transportation%20Statistics%20shows%20US%20airlines%20made%20roughly%20%245.5%20billion%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairline-checked-bag-price-increase-delta-united-jet-blue-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevenue%20from%20checked%20bag%3C%2Fa%3E%20fees%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChanges%20there%20tend%20to%20be%20stickier%20regardless%20of%20the%20demand%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20Sath%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20should%20be%20a%20while%20before%20bag%20fees%20increase%20further%20if%20oil%20prices%20are%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-prices-stay-high-despite-us-peace-deal-iran-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781640104000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a319672564c774507cd3143%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-prices-stay-high-despite-us-peace-deal-iran-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Analysts%20say%20tight%20seat%20supply%20and%20strong%20demand%20give%20airlines%20little%20incentive%20to%20cut%20fares%2C%20even%20if%20the%20US-Iran%20war%20ends%20and%20oil%20prices%20fall.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22trains%40businessinsider.com%20(Taylor%20Rains)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20Trump%20listening%2C%20PM%20Modi%20says%20seafarers%20must%20be%20protected%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781639938000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22ht