20revived%20NO%20FAKES%20Act%2C%20an%20anti-deepfake%20bill%20that%20would%20give%20individuals%20control%20over%20how%20their%20name%20and%20likeness%20are%20used.%20Deepfakes%20have%20been%20a%20constant%20presence%20in%20the%20AI%20age%20as%20large-language%20models%20have%20made%20generating%20depictions%20of%20actors%2C%20singers%20and%20other%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Corbin%20Bolies%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Microsoft%20walked%20away%20from%20a%20%243%20billion%20deal%20to%20lease%20Oracle%20cloud%20capacity%20over%20security%20concerns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222307%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Microsoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a316be173f469f2923c6592%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221539%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMicrosoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella.%3Cp%3EJASON%20REDMOND%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMicrosoft%20wanted%20to%20lease%20Oracle's%20cloud%2C%20sources%20say.%20The%20deal%20could%20have%20been%20worth%20more%20than%20%243%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOracle%20didn't%20want%20to%20add%20a%20security%20framework%20to%20handle%20U.S.%20government%20data%20to%20its%20public%20cloud.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMicrosoft%20walked%20away%20from%20the%20deal%20and%20is%20exploring%20other%20options.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fmicrosoft%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20recently%20in%20talks%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Foracle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOracle%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20leasing%20the%20company's%20cloud%20infrastructure%2C%20but%20the%20deal%20fell%20through%20due%20to%20security%20and%20compliance%20concerns%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20people%20said%20that%20the%20deal%20could%20have%20been%20worth%20more%20than%20%243%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20failed%20talks%20highlight%20a%20growing%20reality%20of%20the%20AI%20boom%3A%20even%20the%20world's%20largest%20technology%20companies%20are%20running%20short%20on%20computing%20power.%20As%20demand%20for%20AI%20services%20soars%2C%20cloud%20providers%20like%20Microsoft%20are%20increasingly%20competing%20not%20just%20for%20customers%20but%20for%20the%20infrastructure%20and%20capacity%20needed%20to%20run%20their%20own%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20scramble%20is%20driving%20an%20unusual%20wave%20of%20partnerships%2C%20capacity-sharing%20agreements%2C%20and%20multibillion-dollar%20infrastructure%20deals%20as%20companies%20race%20to%20secure%20enough%20computing%20resources%20to%20support%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20recently%20projected%20that%20its%20capital%20expenditures%20for%20the%202026%20calendar%20year%20will%20reach%20%24190%20billion%2C%20largely%20to%20expand%20data%20center%20capacity.%20The%20company%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-github-amazon-ai-cloud-capacity-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealready%20turned%20to%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20add%20capacity%20for%20its%20GitHub%20code%20development%20business%20to%20address%20recent%20outages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20is%20seeking%20a%20deal%20or%20deals%20with%20other%20cloud%20providers%20to%20prioritize%20its%20own%20Azure%20cloud%20computing%20resources%20on%20customers%2C%20the%20people%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20shopping%20for%20capacity%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20was%20to%20move%20some%20Microsoft%20workloads%20to%20Oracle%20Cloud%20Infrastructure%2C%20but%20Oracle's%20public%20cloud%20did%20not%20have%20the%20Federal%20Risk%20and%20Authorization%20Management%20Program%20(FedRAMP)%2C%20a%20standardized%20security%20framework%20that%20ensures%20cloud%20services%20are%20secure%20enough%20to%20handle%20U.S.%20government%20data.%20Oracle%20was%20not%20willing%20to%20add%20this%20framework%2C%20one%20of%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20details%20mentioned%20in%20the%20article%20are%20inaccurate%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Oracle%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20declining%20to%20specify%20the%20inaccuracies.%20Microsoft%20is%20both%20an%20OCI%20partner%20and%20a%20customer.%20We%20have%20a%20tremendously%20collaborative%20and%20fruitful%20partnership%2C%20where%20we%20often%20talk%20about%20ways%20we%20can%20expand%20upon%20our%20ongoing%20work%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Oracle%20executive%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20adding%20FedRAMP%20to%20Oracle's%20public%20cloud%20(versus%20its%20government%20cloud%2C%20which%20already%20meets%20it)%20would%20be%20a%20massive%20engineering%20lift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20is%20still%20evaluating%20and%20exploring%20options%20for%20leasing%20cloud%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20talks%20said.%20Amazon%20and%20Google's%20public%20clouds%20have%20FedRAMP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20big%20tech%20companies%20have%20been%20making%20similar%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20and%20Google%20recently%20disclosed%20a%20new%20deal%20in%20which%20Google%20will%20pay%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-spacex-deal-920-million-month-compute-capacity-gemini-enterprise-2026-6%23%3A~%3Atext%3DGoogle%2520to%2520Pay%2520SpaceX%2520%2524920%2Cfor%2520Compute%2520Capacity%2520%252D%2520Business%2520Insider%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESpaceX%20%24920%20million%20a%20month%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20AI%20compute%20capacity%20from%20October%202026%20to%20June%202029.%20That%20emerged%20just%20two%20mon