Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-am-a-stay-at-home-dad-have-best-job-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egood%20dad%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Other%20days%2C%20like%20that%20tea%20party%20day%2C%20not%20so%20much.%20These%20moments%20of%20parenthood%20are%20undeniably%20fleeting.%20There%20are%20days%20when%20I%20look%20at%20my%20kids%20and%20think%20about%20how%20many%20times%20I%20was%20busy%20and%20missed%20the%20little%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I%20enter%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheres-how-to-recognize-the-signs-of-a-friend-crisis-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emental%20spiral%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20everything%20I've%20done%20wrong%2C%20and%20feel%20the%20guilt%20crushing%20me.%20When%20my%20daughter%20asked%20me%20to%20join%20her%20tea%20party%2C%20should%20I%20have%20stopped%20what%20I%20was%20doing%2C%20called%20off%20work%2C%20and%20joined%20in%3F%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20answer%20depends%20on%20so%20many%20things%20%E2%80%94%20if%20I'm%20under%20a%20deadline%20at%20work%2C%20if%20she%20can%20wait%20until%20later%20that%20day%2C%20if%20this%20is%20the%20first%20tea%20party%20I've%20said%20no%20to%20this%20week%20or%20the%2010th.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20finally%20take%20a%20break%2C%20I%20feel%20guilty%2C%20like%20I'm%20selfish%20for%20not%20having%20infinite%20reserves%20of%20patience%20and%20energy.%20But%20the%20guilt%20dissipates%20as%20I%20realize%20I'm%20allowed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchild-focused-parenting-bad-for-kids-parents-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeel%20exhausted%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20being%20needed%20so%20completely.%20I'm%20allowed%20to%20want%20a%20breather%20without%20it%20diminishing%20my%20love%20for%20my%20kids.%20And%20what%20a%20privilege%20it%20is%20to%20be%20needed%20in%20this%20way.%20They%20are%20my%20everything.%20And%2C%20sometimes%2C%20they%20just%20need%20to%20go%20to%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20my%20standard%20as%20a%20good%20dad%20is%20being%20present%20in%20my%20kids'%20lives%2C%20there%20are%20going%20to%20be%20days%20when%20I%20don't%20meet%20that%20standard.%20And%20it's%20true%20for%20us%20all.%20No%20matter%20how%20much%20we%20try%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing%2C%20there%20are%20times%20we%20are%20going%20to%20fall%20short%E2%80%94at%20least%20to%20our%20standards.%20We're%20never%20going%20to%20measure%20up.%20Why%3F%20Because%20we're%20good%20fathers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a5347a2f-d840-4e3b-b1d8-21545af1eeab%5C%22%3EDads%20need%20rest%2C%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgolf-taught-me-how-to-regulate-my-emotions-mental-health-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplayed%20golf%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20I%20was%20a%20teenager%2C%20and%20one%20summer%2C%20I%20spent%20countless%20hours%20practicing%20for%20a%20tournament.%20On%20tournament%20day%2C%20I%20was%20burned%20out.%20My%20mental%20mistakes%20stacked%20up%2C%20and%20frustration%20consumed%20me.%20My%20coach%20pulled%20me%20aside%20afterward%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTake%20some%20time%20off.%20Practice%2C%20but%20don't%20overdo%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20his%20advice%2C%20and%20a%20week%20later%2C%20I%20won%20my%20first%20tournament%20of%20the%20season.%20The%20difference%20wasn't%20skill%3B%20it%20was%20rest%20and%20self-awareness.%20Golf%20is%20hard%2C%20just%20like%20parenting.%20Even%20the%20professionals%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-nyc-from-london-mistakes-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erookie%20mistakes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20bad%20games%20don't%20make%20bad%20golfers%2C%20and%20bad%20days%20don't%20make%20bad%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParenting%20is%20a%20marathon%2C%20not%20a%20sprint%2C%20and%20your%20love%20for%20your%20children%20isn't%20measured%20by%20how%20perfect%20you%20are%20on%20the%20hardest%20days.%20It's%20measured%20by%20showing%20up%2C%20