the%20bite-sized%20candies%20slightly%20crushed%20and%20evenly%20dispersed%20throughout%20the%20vanilla%20soft%20serve.%20It%20was%20a%20simple%20yet%20satisfying%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20this%20Blizzard%20was%20pretty%20underwhelming%2C%20especially%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20other%20ones%20on%20the%20menu.%20I%20think%20it%20could've%20benefited%20from%20the%20addition%20of%20brownie%20chunks%20to%20make%20the%20chocolate%20flavor%20of%20the%20candies%20stand%20out%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERoyal%20Rocky%20Road%20Trip%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223331%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rocky%20road%20blizzard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f3aa0a5e89ebf001f04539a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222498%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoyal%20Rocky%20Road%20Trip%20Blizzard.%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFull%20disclosure%3A%20I%20don't%20care%20much%20for%20rocky-road%20ice%20cream%2C%20so%20I%20knew%20I%20wasn't%20going%20to%20be%20wild%20about%20this%20one%20from%20the%20start.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20Blizzard%20contains%20all%20the%20essential%20flavors%20typically%20found%20in%20rocky-road%20ice%20cream%3A%20chocolate%2C%20peanuts%2C%20and%20marshmallow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20dessert%20also%20contained%20brownie%20chunks%2C%20plus%20a%20gooey%20marshmallow%20core%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20cup.%20I%20can%20see%20this%20being%20a%20dream%20for%20anyone%20who%20loves%20marshmallows%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20that%20the%20core%20overpowered%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Blizzard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20I%20thought%20the%20peanuts%20were%20missing%2C%20but%20they'd%20really%20just%20collected%20at%20the%20very%20bottom%20of%20the%20cup%2C%20which%20made%20every%20bite%20pretty%20inconsistent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EVery%20Cherry%20Chip%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22978%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Very%20Che