3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20still%20confused%20about%20what%20the%20Peanut%20Butter%20Cookie%20Dough%20Party%20was%20supposed%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20it%20would%20have%20chunks%20of%20peanut-butter%20cookie%20dough%2C%20but%20it%20actually%20contained%20chocolate-chip%20cookie%20dough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeanut-butter%20topping%20was%20swirled%20into%20DQ's%20signature%20vanilla%20soft%20serve%20and%20%E2%80%94%20even%20more%20confusing%20%E2%80%94%20it%20had%20a%20crunchy%20peanut-brittle%20topping%20and%20sprinkles%2C%20which%2C%20for%20me%2C%20just%20added%20an%20awkward%20crunchiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it%20wasn't%20bad.%20The%20sauce%20was%20blended%20so%20seamlessly%20into%20the%20vanilla%20soft%20serve%20that%20it%20tasted%20like%20peanut-butter%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20think%20DQ%20would%20be%20better%20off%20pairing%20peanut%20butter%20with%20something%20that%20contrasts%20its%20nutty%20flavor%20more%2C%20like%20dark-chocolate%20brownies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWonder%20Woman%20Cookie%20Collision%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wonder%20Woman%20Cookie%20Collision%202%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f3aa191e89ebf001f0453a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWonder%20Woman%20Cookie%20Collision%20Blizzard.%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20such%20a%20fun%20name%2C%20I%20had%20high%20hopes%20for%20this%20limited-edition%20Blizzard.%20Unfortunately%2C%20it%20underwhelmed%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEssentially%2C%20it's%20a%20hodgepodge%20of%20chocolaty%20flavors.%20Mix-ins%20include%20chocolate-chip%20and%20chocolate-chocolate%20cookie%20dough%2C%20which%20were%20pretty%20much%20indistinguishable%20from%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20had%20potential%2C%20but%20the%20similar%20toppings%20didn't%20add%20much%20flavor.%20I%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20distinguishing%20this%20from%20the%20regular%20cookie-dough%20Blizzard%2C%20which%20is%20disappointing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHeath%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Heath%20Blizzard%20Dairy%20Queen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f3aa209e89ebf001f0453b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeath%20Blizzard.%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20eager%20to%20try%20the%20Blizzard%20because%20I%20think%20Heath%20is%20an%20excellent%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiscontinued-chocolates-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderrated%20candy%20bar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Heath%20candy%20bits%20were%20finely%20chopped%20and%20distributed%20well%20throughout%20the%20soft%20serve.%20This%20gave%20the%20entire%20Blizzard%20a%20strong%20toffee%20taste%2C%20which%20I%20personally%20loved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20biggest%20issue%20with%20this%20one%20was%20the%20texture.%20Toffee%20is%20notoriously%20sticky%20and%20hard%2C%20especially%20when%20paired%20with%20a%20cold%20substance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20ate%20my%20Blizzard%2C%20I%20noticed%20small%20bits%20of%20the%20candy%20getting%20stuck%20to%20my%20teeth%2C%20which%20made%20me%20unwilling%20to%20finish%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOreo%20Dirt%20Pie%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oreo%20Dirt%20Pie%20%20Blizzard%20with%20gummy%20worms%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fd13c1f1df7e0018eae871%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20never%20attended%20summer%20camp%20myself%2C%20I%20have%20many%20fond%20childhood%20memories%20of%20eating%20Oreo%20dirt%20pies%20at%20birthday%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENormally%2C%20the%20dessert%20is%20made%20using%20pudding%20as%20a%20base%2C%20but%20here%2C%20DQ%20is%20putting%20its%20own%20spin%20on%20this%20with%20its%20soft%20serve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20appreciate%20the%20sentiment%20DQ%20was%20trying%20to%20convey%20here%2C%20and%20I'm%20sure%20kids%20will%20go%20nuts%20for%20this%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20sold%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20gummy%20worms%20mixed%20into%20soft%20serve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20topping%2C%20gummy%20worms%20are%20fine.%20However%2C%20I%20didn't%20care%20for%20getting%20random%20bites%20of%20chewy%20candy%20in%20my%20Blizzard.%20There%20was%20already%20enough%20texture%20from%20the%20cookie%20pieces%20and%20fudge.%20Plus%2C%20it's%20not%20like%20the%20gummies%20added%20that%20much%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20more%20positive%20note%2C%20I%20loved%20how%20the%20added%20extra%20fudge%20crumbles%20really%20doubled%20down%20on%20the%20chocolate%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20I'd%20much%20rather%20get%20the%20regular%20Oreo%20Cookie%20Blizzard%2C%20which%20tastes%20similar%20but%20has%20no%20unpleasant%20gummy-worm%20additions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENestl%C3%A9%20Drumstick%20with%20Peanuts%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dairy%20queen%20blizzard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60b63845bee0fc0019d5a9ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20Blizzard%20brought%20me%20back%20to%20childhood%20days%20at%20my%20grandma's%20house%2C%20where%20I'd%20often%20dig%20in%20her%20freezer%20in%20search%20of%20chocolaty%20Drumsticks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20every%20time%2C%20I'd%20devour%20the%20cone%20in%20minutes%2C%20and%20my%20fingers%20(and%20the%20floor)%20would%20end%20up%20covered%20in%20chocolate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20later%2C%20I'm%20still%20a%20fan%20of%20Drumsticks%2C%20but%20I%20rarely%20eat%20them%20to%20avoid%20the%20mess.%20Thankfully%2C%20DQ%20has%20largely%20solved%20that%20issue%20by%20creating%20a%20Blizzard%20with%20Drumstick%20bits%20blended%20right%20in%20that%20I%20can%20enjoy%20with%20the%20convenience%20of%20a%20spoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20let%20me%20tell%20you%2C%20it%20did%20not%20disappoint.%20As%20is%20the%20case%20with%20most%20of%20its%20Blizzards%2C%20the%20vanilla%20soft%20serve%20made%20for%20the%20perfect%20base%2C%20accentuating%20the%20peanut-waffle-cone-Nestl%C3%A9%20chocolate%20flavor%20in%20the%20mix-ins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeanut%20was%20definitely%20the%20predominant%20flavor%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20so%20overpowering%20that%20I%20didn't%20taste%20the%20chocolate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wish%20the%20peanut%20bits%20were%20larger%2C%20though%2C%20since%20they%20kept%20getting%20stuck%20in%20my%20teeth.%20I%20understand%20the%20peanuts%20on%20a%20drumstick%20are%20tiny%20as%20is%2C%20so%20there%20was%20no%20changing%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecreated-favorite-after-school-peanut-butter-treat-as-an-adult-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeanut-butter%20dessert%3C%2Fa%3E%20that's%20not%20too%20chocolaty%20or%20sweet%2C%20try%20this%20Blizzard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPicnic%20Peach%20Cobbler%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223292%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Picnic%20Peach%20Cobbler%20Blizzard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666afb38764df16112596780%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222469%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPicnic%20Peach%20Cobbler%20Blizzard.%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20mind%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffood-reporter-shares-favorite-dessert-recipes-from-over-the-years-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeach%20cobbler%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20usually%20served%20warm%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20topped%20with%20ice%20cream%2C%20so%20I%20was%20curious%20about%20this%20deconstructed%20Blizzard%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20this%20was%20so-so.%20The%20tiny%20chunks%20of%20cold%20cobbler%20were%20easily%20the%20star%20of%20the%20show%2C%20offering%20a%20buttery%20flavor%20that%20was%20delicious%20against%20DQ's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-burger-king-wendys-best-soft-serve-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebasic%20vanilla%20soft%20serve%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20shortbread-like%20texture%20that%20was%20pleasantly%20crumbly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20the%20peach-topping%20swirls%20worked%20for%20me.%20It%20could%20have%20been%20how%20my%20Blizzard%20was%20mixed%2C%20but%20I%20found%20the%20flavor%20distribution%20to%20be%20wildly%20inconsistent%20%E2%80%94%20I%20had%20to%20dig%20around%20before%20I%20got%20any%20peach%20flavor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOreo%20Cookie%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22oreo%20cookie%20blizzard%20dairy%20queen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f3aa4b4e89ebf001f0453e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222592%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOreo%20cookie%20Blizzard.%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20enjoyed%20this%20Blizzard%2C%20it%20seemed%20super%20similar%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-oreo-frozen-dessert-mcdonalds-dairy-queen-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecookies-and-cream%20ice%20cream%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20positive%20note%2C%20DQ's%20signature%20vanilla%20soft%20serve%20tasted%20mellower%20and%20had%20a%20more%20delicate%20finish%20than%20what%20you'd%20find%20at%20the%20grocery%20store.%20I%20also%20liked%20that%20I%20could%20taste%20the%20Oreo%20icing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20probably%20wouldn't%20order%20this%20one%20again%20unless%20I%20was%20on%20the%20go%20and%20craving%20something%20familiar.%20For%20the%20price%2C%20I%20would%20rather%20purchase%20a%20pint%20of%20high-quality%20cookies-and-cream%20ice%20cream%20from%20the%20grocery%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMixing%20Bowl%20Mashup%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Beige%20DQ%20Blizzard%20with%20chocolate%20flecks%20-%20Mixing%20Bowl%20Mashup%20Blizzard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f3d53b5d203112923e3e70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Mixing%20Bowl%20Mashup%20Blizzard%20contains%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20its%20name%2C%20I%20expected%20this%20would%20contain%20a%20mix%20of%20brownie%20and%20cookie-dough%20chunks%2C%20but%20I%20only%20found%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dough%20provided%20more%20texture%20than%20flavor%20under%20the%20blend%20of%20vanilla%20and%20chocolaty%20brownie-batter%20soft%20serve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20anything%2C%20this%20tasted%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwendys-mcdonalds-feud-frosty-one-dollar-deal-mcflurry-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWendy's%20Frosty%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20me%20%E2%80%94%20not%20bad%2C%20just%20underwhelming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUltimate%20Cookie%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ultimate%20Cookie%20Blizzard%20in%20cup%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666afbe5e079049018189c76%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUltimate%20Cookie%20Blizzard.%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIntroduced%20in%202024%20as%20June's%20Blizzard%20of%20the%20Month%2C%20this%20Ultimate%20Cookie%20Blizzard%20is%20made%20for%20people%20who%20appreciate%20lots%20of%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeaturing%20a%20blend%20of%20vanilla%20soft%20serve%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fantarctica-oreos-2012-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENabisco's%20finest%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Chips%20Ahoy%2C%20Oreos%2C%20and%20Nutter%20Butters%20%E2%80%94%20every%20spoonful%20from%20start%20to%20finish%20contained%20some%20bit%20of%20cookie%20chunk.%20Yum!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-brand-chocolate-chip-cookies-should-you-buy-at-grocery-store%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChips%20Ahoy%20cookies%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20barely%20detectable%20under%20the%20flavor%20from%20the%20Nutter%20Butter%20and%20rich%20cocoa%20notes%20coming%20from%20the%20Oreos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20complaining%20because%20it's%20all%20tasty%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn't%20call%20this%20as%20memorable%20or%20impressive%20as%20the%20Oreo%20Brookie%20Blizzard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EChoco%20Brownie%20Extreme%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Choco%20Brownie%20Extreme%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f3aa54de89ebf001f0453f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChoco%20Brownie%20Extreme%20Blizzard.%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20chocolate%20lover%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20that%20I%20didn't%20like%20this%20one%20as%20much%20as%20I'd%20hoped.%20This%20Blizzard%20is%20proof%20that%20there%20can%20be%20too%20much%20of%20a%20good%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20with%20brownie%20pieces%2C%20chocolate%20fudge%2C%20and%20chocolate%20chunks.%20I%20enjoy%20all%20those%20things%20individually%2C%20but%20it's%20almost%20too%20much%20when%20they're%20all%20packed%20together%20in%20an%208-ounce%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20clear%20to%20me%20that%20the%20chewy%20brownie%20chunks%20were%20the%20star%20of%20the%20show%2C%20and%20the%20other%20two%20chocolaty%20components%20didn't%20add%20much.%20The%20brownies%20were%20so%20fudgy%20that%20they%20blended%20together%20with%20the%20fudge%20chunks%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20me%20feels%20like%20the%20fudge%20chunks%20were%20thrown%20in%20just%20to%20give%20this%20Blizzard%20its%20%26quot%3Bextreme%26quot%3B%20name.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kicker%20of%20this%20dessert%20is%20that%20it%20came%20with%20vanilla%20soft%20serve%20%E2%80%94%20not%20chocolate%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20honestly%20couldn't%20taste%20it%20underneath%20all%20of%20the%20toppings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EButterfinger%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22butterfinger%20blizzard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f3aa5eae89ebf001f0453f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EButterfinger%20Blizzard.%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20Blizzard%20consists%20of%20vanilla%20soft%20serve%20and%20a%20generous%20amount%20of%20nutty%2C%20scrumptious%20Butterfinger%20bits.%20I%20immediately%20noticed%20the%20little%20orange%20bits%20sticking%20out%20of%20the%20creamy%20soft%20serve%20when%20it%20was%20handed%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaste-wise%2C%20this%20Blizzard%20was%20good%20but%20not%20incredible.%20The%20candy%20bar%20seemed%20ground%20to%20a%20fine%20powder%2C%20allowing%20the%20nutty%20flavor%20to%20blend%20seamlessly%20into%20the%20soft%20serve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20felt%20the%20candy's%20chocolate%20coating%20got%20completely%20lost%20in%20the%20mixing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESnickers%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22snickers%20blizzard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f3aa649e89ebf001f0453f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height