na%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPuppy%20chow%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%26quot%3Bmuddy%20buddies%26quot%3B%20depending%20on%20where%20you%20grew%20up%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20common%20snack%20at%20many%20a%20childhood%20sleepover%2C%20movie%20night%2C%20holiday%20party%2C%20or%20school%20event.%20It's%20a%20treat%20made%20using%20basic%20cereal%20like%20Chex%2C%20melted%20chocolate%2C%20peanut%20butter%2C%20and%20powdered%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20surprised%20Dairy%20Queen%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20mix-in.%20Still%2C%20I%20wasn't%20blown%20away%20by%20this%20flavor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20tasty%2C%20and%20the%20peanut-butter%20flavor%20came%20through%20nicely%20on%20every%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20my%20order%2C%20the%20few%20squares%20of%20puppy%20chow%20in%20the%20mix%20were%20clumped%20toward%20the%20bottom.%20When%20I%20did%20eat%20a%20piece%2C%20though%2C%20it%20was%20delicious%20and%20nicely%20softened%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20soft%20serve%20while%20still%20retaining%20a%20slight%20crispiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pieces%20also%20seemed%20to%20add%20a%20subtle%20salty%20taste%20that%20I%20felt%20was%20missing%20with%20the%20Reese's%20Peanut%20Butter%20Cup%20Blizzard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOreo%20Fudge%20Brownie%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223610%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22oreo%20fudge%20brownie%20blizzard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f3aa716e89ebf001f045404%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOreo%20fudge%20brownie%20Blizzard.%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20chain's%20traditional%20Oreo%20Cookie%20Blizzard%2C%20this%20comes%20with%20vanilla%20soft%20serve%20and%20chewy%20Oreo%20bits.%20The%20main%20difference%20is%20that%20this%20takes%20the%20Blizzard%20to%20the%20next%20level%20by%20adding%20fudge%20and%20yummy%20brownie%20pieces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20good%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20much%20of%20a%20standout%20to%20me%20because%20the%20Oreos%20seemed%20to%20fade%20into%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brownies%20dominated%20the%20dessert%2C%20which%20wasn't%20a%20problem%20for%20me%20as%20a%20chocolate%20lover%2C%20but%20it%20made%20me%20question%20whether%20the%20Oreos%20were%20necessary%20at%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETurtle%20Pecan%20Cluster%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222931%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tyrtle%20pecan%20dairy%20q%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f3aa772e89ebf001f045409%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222198%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETurtle%20pecan%20cluster%20Blizzard.%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20blend%20of%20buttery%20pecans%2C%20caramel%2C%20and%20vanilla%20on%20this%20Blizzard%20was%20absolutely%20divine.%20I%20also%20liked%20that%20my%20order%20contained%20pieces%20of%20whole%20pecans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20found%20the%20chocolate%20fudge%20shavings%20to%20be%20unnecessary%20because%20they%20weren't%20noticeable%20at%20all.%20That%20said%2C%20this%20Blizzard%20earns%20high%20marks%20for%20its%20uniqueness%20and%20great%20taste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECaramel%20Drumstick%20with%20Peanuts%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Caramel%20Drumstick%20with%20Peanuts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fd1310f1df7e0018eae819%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaramel%20Drumstick%20Blizzard%20with%20peanuts.%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20be%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BWait%20a%20second%2C%20Dairy%20Queen%20has%20always%20had%20a%20Drumstick%20Blizzard%20with%20peanuts.%26quot%3B%20Correct.%20This%20one%20is%20different%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20all%20that%20%3Cem%3Eand%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecaramel.%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisually%2C%20it%20looks%20no%20different%20from%20the%20other%20Drumstick%20Blizzard.%20However%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20took%20that%20first%20bite%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20this%20was%20a%20huge%20step%20above%20the%20original.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20caramel%20topping%20was%20blended%20seamlessly%20into%20the%20soft%20serve%2C%20offering%20a%20tasty%20touch%20of%20sweetness%20that%20paired%20incredibly%20well%20with%20the%20peanuts%20and%20chocolaty%20Drumstick%20pieces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20all%2C%20it's%20a%20wonderful%20combination%20of%20slightly%20salty%2C%20sweet%2C%20and%20nutty%20flavors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20who%20are%20hoping%20to%20get%20huge%20globs%20of%20gooey%20caramel%20might%20be%20disappointed.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20want%20something%20that's%20delicious%20and%20sweet%20but%20not%20quite%20as%20intense%20as%20some%20of%20the%20candy-flavored%20Blizzards%2C%20this%20will%20hit%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOreo%20Brookie%20Blizzard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oreo%20brookie%20blizzard%20with%20red%20spoon%20sticking%20out%20of%20it%20in%20a%20blue%20dairy%20queen%20cup%20in%20a%20car%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64aeee1b94be880019f3a48c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOreo%20brookie%20Blizzard.%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Swain-Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20when%20you%20think%20DQ%20hasn't%20done%20enough%20with%20Oreo%2C%20the%20chain%20adds%20tiny%2C%20dime-sized%20chunks%20of%20brownie-and-chocolate-chip-cookie%20hybrids.%20The%20more%20cookies%2C%20the%20better.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20the%20first%20spoonful%2C%20I%20thought%20this%20Blizzard%20tasted%20like%20a%20typical%20cookies-and-cream%20one.%20Once%20I%20got%20a%20piece%20of%20the%20brookie%2C%20though%2C%20I%20understood%20why%20this%20was%20s