e%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20chain%20has%20struggled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELongRange%20is%20pitching%20itself%20as%20a%20hands-on%20operator%20rather%20than%20a%20financial%20buyer.%20In%20a%20statement%20announcing%20the%20deal%2C%20the%20firm%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20invest%20in%20Pizza%20Hut's%20growth%20and%20build%20on%20its%20franchise%20system%20and%20global%20footprint.%20Yum%20said%20Pizza%20Hut%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bwell%20positioned%20for%20future%20growth%26quot%3B%20under%20LongRange%20and%20Yum%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20message%20will%20be%20critical%20for%20workers%20and%20franchisees%20evaluating%20the%20chain's%20new%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20know%20it's%20being%20bought%20by%20private%20equity%2C%20so%20they%20already%20know%20that%20means%20things%20are%20going%20to%20have%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Cerda%20said.%20The%20challenge%20for%20LongRange%2C%20she%20said%2C%20will%20be%20balancing%20those%20changes%20with%20a%20convincing%20case%20that%20the%20investment%20is%20meant%20to%20%26quot%3Bre-energize%20and%20revitalize%20the%20brand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20two%20transactions%2C%20Yum%20expects%20to%20receive%20about%20%242.3%20billion%20in%20net%20proceeds%20after%20taxes%2C%20closing%20adjustments%2C%20and%20transaction-related%20fees%2C%20excluding%20a%20potential%20%2475%20million%20earn-out%20by%202030.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20expects%20roughly%20%2485%20million%20in%20one-time%20costs%20to%20complete%20the%20separation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20comes%20as%20Pizza%20Hut%20faces%20challenges%20beyond%20slowing%20sales.%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20that%20Yum%20planned%20to%20close%20250%20underperforming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frestaurant-chains-closing-locations-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPizza%20Hut%20locations%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20first%20half%20of%202026.%20In%20May%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-pizza-chains-in-the-us-yelp-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPizza%20Hut%20franchisee%3C%2Fa%3E%20sued%20the%20chain%20over%20its%20Dragontail%20restaurant%20management%20system%2C%20alleging%20it%20caused%20operational%20disruptions%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpizza-hut-ai-system-dragontail-lawsuit-franchisee-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustomer%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpizza-hut-ai-system-dragontail-lawsuit-franchisee-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Pizza%20Hut%20said%20at%20the%20time%20it%20was%20reviewing%20the%20claims%20and%20would%20respond%20through%20the%20appropriate%20legal%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Yum%2C%20the%20sale%20sharpens%20its%20focus%20on%20its%20other%20brands%3A%20KFC%2C%20Taco%20Bell%2C%20and%20Habit%20Burger%20%26amp%3B%20Grill.%20For%20LongRange%2C%20it%20is%20a%20bet%20that%20operational%20improvements%20can%20revive%20a%20chain%20whose%20red%20roof%20remains%20iconic%20while%20its%20business%20has%20struggled%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aktl%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ektl%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20byktl.50.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3