ot%3Bsuper%20app%26quot%3B%20beyond%20streaming%2C%20a%20top%20exec%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%20on%20the%20road%20map%20about%20bringing%20either%20cruises%20or%20the%20parks%20into%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInstead%2C%20he%20said%20Disney%20is%20focused%20on%20integrating%20Hulu%20into%20Disney%2B.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20isn't%20building%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20app%26quot%3B%20tying%20together%20all%20its%20businesses%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20not%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdam%20Smith%2C%20the%20chief%20product%20and%20technology%20officer%20for%20Disney%20Entertainment%20and%20ESPN%2C%20told%20employees%20at%20a%20town%20hall%20last%20week%20that%20the%20company%20isn't%20planning%20to%20turn%20Disney%2B%20into%20a%20hub%20for%20buying%20tickets%20to%20parks%20and%20cruises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20moment%2C%20I%20can%20definitively%20say%20there%20is%20nothing%20on%20the%20road%20map%20about%20bringing%20either%20cruises%20or%20the%20parks%20into%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recording%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20Smith%20was%20responding%20to%20an%20employee-submitted%20question%20about%20making%20Disney%2B%20a%20so-called%20super%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2026-05-01%2Fdisney-is-exploring-a-super-app-for-theme-park-tickets-movies-and-more%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%20that%20Disney%20was%20exploring%20turning%20its%20flagship%20streaming%20service%20into%20%26quot%3Bthe%20first%20stop%20for%20all%20things%20Disney%26quot%3B%20where%20fans%20could%20buy%20park%20tickets%2C%20merchandise%2C%20and%20play%20games%20in%20between%20streaming%20shows%2C%20citing%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bloomberg%20report%20added%20that%20conversations%20about%20creating%20this%20potential%20app%20were%20%26quot%3Bat%20an%20early%20stage%20and%20no%20concrete%20steps%20have%20been%20taken%20toward%20developing%20the%20product.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20said%20companies%20%26quot%3Bhave%20seen%20'super%20apps'%20work%26quot%3B%20in%20places%20like%20Asia%2C%20but%20added%20that%20the%20Mouse%20House%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20ways%20off%20from%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Smith%20said%20his%20priority%20is%20turning%20Disney%2B%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-streaming-engagement-viewership-growth-hulu-integration-ai-generated-video-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eone-stop%20shop%20for%20streaming%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20folding%20in%20Hulu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%2C%20really%20want%20to%20land%20this%20work%20with%20bringing%20Hulu%20over%20to%20Disney%2B%20for%20our%20users%20and%20creating%20Disney%2B%2FHulu%20as%20a%20fantastic%20spot%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20began%20adding%20select%20Hulu%20shows%20to%20Disney%2B%20in%20late%202023%20and%20announced%20last%20summer%20that%20it%20would%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-hulu-fully-integrated-new-app-2026-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efully%20integrate%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-hulu-fully-integrated-new-app-2026-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20Hulu%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20its%20namesake%20streamer.%20The%20company%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-hulu-future-streaming-employees-ad-revenue-growth-espn-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecombined%20the%20platforms'%20ad%20servers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20said%20last%20month%20that%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bno%20current%20plans%20to%20sunset%26quot%3B%20the%20Hulu%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20an%20internal%20document%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%20suggested%20that%20the%20streamer's%20days%20as%20a%20stand-alone%20service%20are%20numbered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Hulu%20tech%20stack%20and%20app%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-hulu-app-unification-future-project-gemini-superapp-josh-damaro-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewill%20be%20decommissioned%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20all%20users%20have%20transitioned%26quot%3B%20from%20that%20app%20into%20Disney%2B%2C%20the%20document%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney's%20plan%20to%20integrate%20Hulu%20into%20Disney%2B%20is%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BOne%20Disney%26quot%3B%20initiative%20championed%20by%20CEO%20Josh%20D'Amaro%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-ceo-josh-damaro-first-day-memo-employees-walden-iger-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20his%20inaugural%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20staffers%20that%20aligning%20teams%20across%20the%20company%20is%20a%20priority%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20said%20the%20Hulu%20convergence%20project%2C%20which%20is%20known%20internally%20as%20%26quot%3BProject%20Gemini%2C%26quot%3B%20should%20%26quot%3Breally%20reinforce%20Josh's%20commitment%20to%20this%20cross-Disney%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecutives%20like%20D'Amaro%20and%20Smith%20are%20focused%20on%20how%20best%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-adults-book-fandom-judgment-haters-parks-movies-aj-wolfe-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eserve%20their%20die-hard%20fan%20base%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20product%20and%20tech%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20do%20we%20break%20down%20the%20cultural%20barriers%20and%20work%20as%20One%20Disney%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20our%20fans%20and%20users%20are%20getting%20the%20best%20of%20Disney%2C%20wherever%20they%20show%20up%3F%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney