m%2F6a317435e826bfa433d6e83b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22599%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWeidmann's%20was%20opened%20in%201870%20by%20Felix%20Weidmann%2C%20a%20Swiss%20immigrant.%3Cp%3ERyan%20G.%2FYelp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20restaurant's%20most%20distinctive%20customs%20is%20noticeable%20as%20soon%20as%20customers%20sit%20down%3A%20a%20jar%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-brand-of-peanut-butter-from-grocery-store-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epeanut%20butter%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20an%20assortment%20of%20crackers%20on%20every%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20may%20seem%20unusual%20to%20first-time%20visitors%2C%20the%20practice%20has%20become%20one%20of%20Weidmann's%20signature%20traditions%20and%20a%20beloved%20part%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-knife-and-fork-inn-steakhouse-atlantic-city-value-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehistoric%20steakhouse's%3C%2Fa%3E%20dining%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20dates%20back%20to%20World%20War%20II%2C%20when%20butter%20was%20scarce%20because%20of%20wartime%20rationing%20and%20supply%20shortages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20restaurant%2C%20when%20a%20customer%20mentioned%20to%20then-owner%20Henry%20Weidmann%2C%20Felix's%20grandson%2C%20that%20they%20could%20replace%20traditional%20butter%20with%20peanut%20butter%2C%20which%20was%20more%20widely%20available%2C%20it%20took%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20quickly%20embraced%20the%20substitute%2C%20and%20what%20started%20as%20a%20practical%20response%20to%20a%20wartime%20shortage%20became%20a%20beloved%20restaurant%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20butter%20became%20readily%20available%20again%20following%20the%20war%2C%20customers%20had%20grown%20so%20fond%20of%20the%20combination%20that%20the%20restaurant%20decided%20to%20continue%20the%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDecades%20later%2C%20staff%20still%20place%20a%20jar%20of%20peanut%20butter%20and%20a%20basket%20of%20assorted%20crackers%20on%20every%20table%2C%20preserving%20a%20piece%20of%20the%20restaurant's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223540764b-97d7-4ea4-aa94-b803747d2786%5C%22%3EThey%20weren't%20served%20in%20a%20standard-issue%20peanut%20butter%20jar%2C%20either%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Weidmann's%20Restaurant%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a31792e73f469f2923c6682%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStaff%20still%20place%20a%20jar%20of%20peanut%20butter%20and%20a%20basket%20of%20assorted%20crackers%20on%20every%20table.%3Cp%3EJim%20G.%2FYelp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%201940s%2C%20Henry%20commissioned%20a%20potter%20in%20Louisville%2C%20Mississippi%2C%20to%20make%20peanut-butter%20crocks%20by%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20diners%20are%20encouraged%20to%20spread%20the%20peanut%20butter%2C%20which%20is%20still%20served%20in%20a%20handmade%20ceramic%20crock%2C%20onto%20crackers%20while%20they%20browse%20the%20menu%20and%20wait%20for%20their%20food.%20The%20pre-meal%20snack%20is%20complimentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeidmann's%20is%20also%20known%20for%20classic%20steakhouse%20fare%2C%20including%20crab%20cakes%20and%20hand-cut%20steaks%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Weidmann's%20World%20Famous%20Black%20Bottom%20Pie%2C%20a%20dessert%20with%20a%20gingersnap%20crust%20topped%20with%20a%20layer%20of%20dark%20chocolate%2C%20bourbon%20custard%2C%20and%20whipped%20cream%2C%20introduced%20by%20Henry%20Weidmann.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20famous%20peanut%20butter%20crocks%20are%20now%20handmade%20by%20a%20local%20potter%20in%20Meridian%20and%20available%20for%20purchase%20for%20%2427.50%2C%20according%20to%20the%20restaurant's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weidmanns1870.com%2Fabout-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2080%2