a%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuild-app-no-coding-skills-ai-lovable-replit-claude%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eembraced%20vibe-coding%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20everyday%20routine%20and%20recently%20designed%20multiple%20apps%20that%20have%20reshaped%20how%20he%20organizes%20his%20workday%2C%20manages%20travel%2C%20and%20communicates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20I%20find%20so%20empowering%20about%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20if%20you%20have%20an%20idea%20for%20an%20app%20and%20it's%20literally%20only%20relevant%20to%20you%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolopreneurs-vibe-code-tools-that-help-grow-business-4-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyou%20can%20build%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20few%20hours%20and%20then%20load%20it%20onto%20your%20phone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Smith's%20view%2C%20the%20most%20interesting%20part%20of%20AI%20isn't%20hypothetical%20superintelligence.%20It's%20the%20fact%20that%20people%20can%20already%20use%20it%20to%20automate%20small%20frustrations%20and%20build%20tools%20tailored%20to%20their%20own%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e2007b3-587d-4599-a74b-8c1b9f3b31ee%5C%22%3EApps%20he%20built%20are%20changing%20how%20he%20works%20and%20thinks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226978%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20Charlie%20Smith%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a17193a2e5a80cfe04ff478%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225234%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharlie%20Smith%20is%20the%20chief%20brand%20officer%20of%20consumer-tech%20company%20Nothing.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Nothing%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20recently%20vibe-coded%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-fitness-app-weekend-software-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epersonal%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20one%20that%20combines%20his%20emails%2C%20appointments%2C%20weather%20updates%2C%20and%20news%20coverage%20into%20a%20daily%20dashboard%2C%20and%20another%20that%20organizes%20his%20flight%20and%20boarding%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20been%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20AI-powered%20voice%20tools%20are%20also%20changing%20how%20he%20captures%20ideas%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Nothing%20recently%20launched%20a%20suite%20of%20AI-powered%20tools%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BEssential%20Voice%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20dictation%20tool%20that%20removes%20filler%20words%20and%20restructures%20spoken%20thoughts%20into%20cleaner%20written%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20have%20stopped%20typing%20since%20using%20Essential%20Voice%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230bc184f-b909-4796-a24b-fcdc099e79e1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Nothing%20calls%20its%20AI%20products%20'essential'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENothing's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-workplace-more-productive-less-social-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20focused%20less%20on%20futuristic%20language%20and%20more%20on%20utility%2C%20Smith%20said.%20The%20company%20intentionally%20avoids%20heavily%20emphasizing%20the%20term%20%26quot%3BAI%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20product%20positioning%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20calling%20our%20AI-powered%20products%20essential%20because%20it's%20more%20about%20what%20they%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENothing's%20long-term%20vision%20is%20based%20on%20the%20belief%20that%20devices%20will%20become%20%26quot%3BAI%20native%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20next%20several%20years%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20predicts%20that%20computing%20could%20gradually%20shift%20away%20from%20app-based%20interfaces%20and%20toward%20systems%20that%20automatically%20surface%20information%20based%20on%20a%20user's%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20move%20from%20this%20kind%20of%20app%20world%20to%20a%20more%20agentic%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b9896ed9-d87b-41d8-b06a-c2bfc1591e2e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20fear%20around%20AI%20is%20a%20'branding%20problem'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Smith%20embraces%20AI%20tools%20personally%2C%20he%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20technology%20faces%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-graduates-ai-backlash-commencement-speeches-anxiety-job-market-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egrowing%20skepticism%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20among%20younger%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20believes%20much%20of%20that%20backlash%20comes%20from%20how%20AI%20companies%20market%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20do%20think%20it's%20a%20branding%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Smith%2C%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ai-jobs-prediction-wrong-white-collar-openai-australia-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20executives%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20focused%20heavily%20on%20messaging%20around%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20and%20job%20displacement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20leaders%20in%20tech%20of%20these%20AI%20companies%20are%20really%20talking%20up%20AGI%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20take%20over%20our%20jobs%20in%20order%20to%20inflate%20the%20valuation%20of%20the%20company%20and%20get%20more%20funding%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20said%20he%20does%20not%20believe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-automating-boring-work-killing-creativity-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20will%20eliminate%20human%20creativity%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20replace%20all%20jobs.%