i%3EShe%20bought%20a%20split-level%20house%20for%20us%20to%20live%20in%20together%2C%20and%20we%20cover%20the%20bills%20and%20maintenance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20mom%20has%20her%20own%20space%2C%20plus%20we%20get%20to%20save%20money%20and%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20together%20as%20a%20family.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20after%20my%20dad%20passed%20away%2C%20my%20mom%20made%20a%20decision%20that%20changed%20all%20our%20lives%3A%20She%20was%20going%20to%20sell%20her%20home%20and%20move%20in%20with%20my%20husband%20and%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20almost%2070%20and%20was%20fully%20capable%20of%20living%20on%20her%20own%20%E2%80%94%20she%20just%20didn't%20want%20to%20anymore.%20Her%20decision%20wasn't%20driven%20by%20a%20financial%20or%20health%20crisis%20but%20by%20loneliness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20that%2C%20the%20house%20she%20lived%20in%20needed%20significant%20repairs%2C%20and%20maintaining%20both%20the%20home%20and%20its%20expansive%20property%20had%20become%20overwhelming%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quiet%20privacy%20she%20and%20my%20dad%20once%20loved%20no%20longer%20felt%20comforting%2C%20either.%20With%20no%20neighbors%20in%20sight%20and%20an%20increasing%20presence%20of%20coyotes%20and%20other%20wildlife%2C%20what%20had%20once%20felt%20peaceful%20had%20become%20isolating%20and%2C%20at%20times%2C%20downright%20scary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20very%20open%20to%20living%20with%20my%20mom%2C%20but%20our%20rental%20wasn't%20ideal%20for%20three%20adults.%20So%2C%20we%20agreed%20on%20a%20plan%3A%20She%20would%20purchase%20a%20house%20for%20all%20of%20us%20to%20live%20in%2C%20while%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20would%20pay%20for%20the%20renovations%2C%20utilities%2C%20maintenance%2C%20repairs%2C%20and%20yard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20was%20a%20whirlwind%3A%20a%20quick%20home%20sale%2C%20an%20eight-week%20house%20hunt%2C%20and%20ultimately%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigher-cost-of-living-creating-multigenerational-homes-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emultigenerational%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20worked%20better%20than%20any%20of%20us%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b824d04-bdc5-4967-9639-fc4c707ce270%5C%22%3EAfter%20lots%20of%20searching%2C%20we%20found%20a%20split-level%20house%20that%20could%20work%20for%20our%20needs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20standing%20in%20kitchen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2036152e5a80cfe0502ba1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20photo%20of%20my%20mom%20inside%20one%20of%20the%20homes%20we%20toured%20during%20our%20house%20hunt.%3Cp%3ETonya%20Prater%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20temporarily%20moved%20into%20the%20property%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20renting%20nearby%20while%20we%20searched%20for%20a%20house%20that%20would%20give%20all%20of%20us%20the%20space%20and%20privacy%20we%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20hunt%20for%20a%20home%20with%20an%20existing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-added-in-law-suite-to-home-multigenerational-living-photos-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein-law%20suite%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20a%20space%20we%20could%20easily%20convert%20into%20one%20lasted%20about%20eight%20weeks%2C%20but%20felt%20much%20longer.%20Eventually%2C%20we%20settled%20on%20the%20perfect%20split-level%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20few%20adjustments%2C%20the%20lower%20level%20would%20offer%20the%20perfect%20setup%20for%20my%20mom%20while%20keeping%20us%20all%20under%20one%20roof.%20Unlike%20her%20previous%20house%2C%20this%20one%20had%20air%20conditioning%2C%20a%20washer%20and%20dryer%2C%20and%20a%20large%20sunroom%20where%20she%20could%20relax%20with%20her%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20we%20all%20moved%20in%2C%20my%20husband%20transformed%20the%20lower%20level%20into%20what%20my%20mom%20affectionately%20calls%20her%20%26quot%3Bapartment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222903%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20hanging%20hooks%20on%20shelves%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2036152ab5f9757add86d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222322%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20husband%20has%20made%20some%20updates%20to%20the%20house%20to%20make%20it%20work%20for%20all%20of%20us.%3Cp%3ETonya%20Prater%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20installed%20a%20door%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-living-apart-separate-homes-relationship-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eseparating%20our%20living%20spaces%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20painted%20the%20dark%20wood%20paneling%20the%20cheerful%20yellow%20she%20selected%2C%20built%20custom%20shelves%20for%20her%20books%20and%20collectibles%2C%20and%20added%20a%20kitchenette%20with%20a%20refrigerator%20so%20she%20can%20cook%20her%20own%20meals%20if%20she%20chooses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22105e1257-c6a1-46e9-90f7-30384cf9d54e%5C%22%3EOver%20thep%20past%202%20years%2C%20living%20together%20has%20gone%20better%20than%20we%20imagined%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222025%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20holding%20book%20next%20to%20little%20girl%20and%20woman%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a203615b4fb977f35983b29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221519%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20love%20that%20our%20family%20can%20spend%20more%20time%20together%2C%20and%20our%20grandkids%20have%20gotten%20to%20really%20know%20their%20great-grandmother.%3Cp%3ETonya%20Prater%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20of%20us%20have%20lived%20together%20for%20almost%20two%20years%2C%20and%20the%20arrangement%20has%20gone%20surprisingly%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbove%20all%2C%20I've%20learned%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigher-cost-of-living-creating-multigenerational-homes-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esuccessful%20multigenerational%20living%3C%2Fa%3E%20requires%20respecting%20one%20another's%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20moved%20in%20together%2C%20I%20imagined%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-family-meals-costco-executive-member-grocery-list-recommendations-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efamily%20dinners%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20table%20every%20evening%2C%20or%20on%20the%20deck%20overlooking%20the%20backyard.%20Although%20I%20still%20plan%20meals%20and%20cook%20for%20all%20of%20us%20most%20evenings%2C%20my%20mom%20often%20prefers%20eating%20alone%20in%20her%20apartment.%20And%20that's%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20grandchildren%20understand%20this%2C%20too.%20When%20they%20visit%2C%20they%20knock%20on%20the%20door%20separating%20our%20living%20spaces%20and%20wait%20for%20a%20response%20before%20entering.%20They%20enjoy%20spending%20time%20with%20%26quot%3BDownstairs%20Grandma%26quot%3B%20and%20her%20six%20cats%2C%20but%20they%20also%20understand%20that%20her%20space%20belongs%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20practical%20benefits%20to%20this%20arrangement%20as%20well.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-back-into-childhood-home-adult-40-with-family-good-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eno%20longer%20pay%20rent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Mom%20doesn't%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20upkeeping%20a%20house%20and%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20often%20assume%20multigenerational%20living%20occurs%20because%20of%20a%20financial%20crisis%20or%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-cost-of-caring-for-aging-parents-and-lessons-learned-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaging%20parent's%20medical%20needs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20our%20case%2C%20it%20started%20with%20a%20parent%20who%20simply%20didn't%20want%20to%20live%20in%20isolation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20greatest%20benefit%20isn't%20financial%20or%20practical%20at%20all.%20When%20my%20dad%20died%2C%20I%20was%20left%20wishing%20there%20had%20been%20more%20time%2C%20more%20conversations%2C%20and%20more%20ordinary%20moments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20mom%20passes%20before%20I%20do%2C%20I%20hopefully%20won't%20have%20those%20same%20regrets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20us%20knows%20how%20much%20time%20we%20have%20together%2C%20but%20living%20under%20one%20roof%20has%20given%20us%20more%20of%20it%20%E2%80%94%20more%20everyday%20conversations%2C%20more%20opportunities%20for%20my%20grandchildren%20to%20know%20their%20great-grandmother%2C%20and%20more%20ordinary%20moments%20that%20may%20otherwise%20have%20been%20missed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultigenerational%20living%20isn't%20the%20right%20choice%20for%20every%20family.%20But%20for%20us%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20thoughtful%20decision%20built%20on%20connection%2C%20practicality%2C%20and%20the%20desire%20to%20be%20intentional%20about%20the%20people%20who%20matter%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faging-mom-bought-house-we-moved-in-multigenerational-living-benefits-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781626322000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2036992ab5f9757add86dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faging-mom-bought-house-we-moved-in-multigenerational-living-benefits-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20mom%20bought%20a%20split-level%20house%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20moved%20in%20with%20her.%20The%20multigenerational%20arrangement%20offers%20independence%20and%20financial%20perks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tonya%20Prater)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Group%20planned%20to%20attack%20White%20