nstitutions%20like%20Central%20Food%20Technological%20Research%20Institute%20(CFTRI)%20Mysuru%2C%20and%20Kerala%20Agriculture%20University%20to%20explore%20the%20nutritional%20benefits%20and%20viability%20of%20sprouting%20cashews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20an%20encouraging%20response%20from%20the%20institutes%2C%20his%20focus%20shifted%20towards%20refining%20the%20sprouting%20technology%20for%20cashews.%20Recognising%20the%20perishable%20nature%20of%20cashews%20and%20the%20challenges%20in%20maintaining%20a%20cold%20supply%20chain%2C%20he%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20retorting%20technology%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20which%20involves%20heat-treating%20food%20in%20airtight%20containers%20to%20extend%20shelf%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20adapting%20this%20innovative%20approach%2C%20he%20devised%20a%20method%20to%20process%20and%20store%20sprouted%20cashews%20at%20room%20temperature%2C%20enhancing%20their%20shelf%20life%20and%20market%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20into%20research%20and%20development%2C%20Brijith%20started%20his%20own%20startup%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20raw%20sprouts%2C%20pickles%20to%20manchurian%2C%20soup%20premix%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20initial%20challenges%20that%20Brijith%20tackled%20was%20the%20limited%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews.%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20their%20seasonal%20nature%2C%20the%20germination%20potential%20of%20matured%20cashews%20was%20only%2090%20days.%20Therefore%2C%20year%20round%20availability%20was%20a%20big%20concern.%20Through%20persistent%20research%2C%20trials%2C%20and%20development%20efforts%2C%20I%20successfully%20extended%20the%20germination%20potential%20to%20180-200%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20Brijith%20secured%20a%20grant%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20from%20the%20central%20government%20under%20the%20Rashtriya%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana%20(RKVY)%20scheme%20that%20aims%20at%20promoting%20agri-business%20entrepreneurship.%20This%20helped%20him%20kickstart%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brijith%20foccussed%20on%20improving%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews%20in%20order%20to%20commercialise%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBrijith%20focussed%20on%20improving%20the%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews%20to%20commercialise%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20he%20offers%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20value-added%20products%20%E2%80%93%20cashew%20sprouts%20Manchurian%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20butter%20%3Cem%3Emasala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20%3Cem%3Emalai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20schezwan%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20Malabar%20%3Cem%3Emasala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20%3Cem%3Etheyal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20soup%20premix%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20brine%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20fresh%20cashew%20sprouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20meticulous%20focus%20on%20quality%20and%20value%2C%20Brijith%20priced%20his%20sprouted%20cashews%20at%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20kg.%20Through%20strategic%20partnerships%20with%20celebrity%20chefs%2C%20star%20hotels%2C%20and%20catering%20groups%2C%20Brijith%20positioned%20his%20premium%20cashew%20sprout%20products%20in%20a%20niche%20market%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20regular%20customers%20Thomas%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20corporate%20chef%20at%20Paragon%20group%20of%20restaurants%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20experienced%20these%20cashew%20sprouts%20can%20be%20included%20in%20a%20healthy%20diet%20and%20lots%20of%20various%20dishes%20can%20be%20prepared%20with%20adaptability.%20It%20is%20not%20easily%20available%20in%20stores%20so%20people%20have%20some%20curiosity%20about%20it.%20These%20dishes%20are%20repeatedly%20demanded%20from%20our%20happy%20customers%20at%20the%20restaurant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unique%20positioning%20in%20the%20market%20enabled%20Brijith%20to%20secure%20a%20steady%20clientele%20and%20achieve%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20his%20endeavours%20were%20not%20only%20driven%20by%20a%20passion%20for%20innovation%20but%20also%20by%20a%20commitment%20to%20empower%20local%20farmers.%20By%20purchasing%20wet%20cashews%20from%20at%20least%2011%20local%20farmers%2C%20Brijith%20managed%20to%20provide%20a%20sustainable%20solution%20by%20transforming%20them%20into%20high-quality%20sprouted%20cashews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20reimagining%20traditional%20practices%20and%20leveraging%20modern%20technology%2C%20I%20not%20only%20wanted%20to%20revitalise%20the%20cashew%20farming%20industry%20but%20also%20exemplify%20the%20potential%20for%20agri-business%20entrepreneurship%20to%20drive%20economic%20growth%20in%20rural%20communities.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20wet%20produce%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%2